				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Bi%E1%BB%87t-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-lang-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Wznqw5FOp0EenZgqLf7KjA">Biệt Nguyễn đại lang kỳ 2 - 別阮大郎其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-37/poem-joHSO0KoP6J10TXCVM4eqw">Cảm ngộ kỳ 37 - 感遇其三十七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BA%ADu-xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-aS6pKO9QH3yEtu7KXeebFw">Hậu xuất tái kỳ 5 - 後出塞其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u-Lu%C3%A2n/poem-YorXSjO-Q8X4wyE_Ywou2g">Khốc Vương Bành Châu Luân - 哭王彭州掄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/M%E1%BA%A1ch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-m%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n/poem-K2eoDFQpP67xpP0-hnfxig">Mạch thượng tặng mỹ nhân - 陌上贈美人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-%C3%A1i-ch%C3%BAng/poem-vRbxRLFOPBjm83wKLfI8Qw">Phiếm ái chúng - 泛愛眾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%